1. *Ogledalo* mi se razbilo na komade. (The mirror broke into pieces.)
2. Ovaj *ogledalni* efekat stvara optičku iluziju. (This mirror effect creates an optical illusion.)
3. *Ogledala* na zidu čine prostor većim. (Mirrors on the wall make the space look bigger.)
4. Imao je običaj da se *ogleda* u izlogu prodavnice. (He had a habit of checking his reflection in the store window.)
5. Ukoliko želite da kupite *ogledalo*, posetite našu prodavnicu. (If you want to buy a mirror, visit our store.)
6. *Ogledalo* se nalazilo na komodi pored kreveta. (The mirror was located on the nightstand next to the bed.)
7. Možete li mi pozajmiti *ogledalo* za minut? (Can you lend me the mirror for a minute?)
8. Dete se smejalo dok se *ogledalo* u vodi. (The child laughed while looking at his reflection in the water.)